{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418870/extras/follow_whitelist.gif?t=1728265205\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Wild West has been invaded by powerful slimes, and it's up to you to defend it. In &quot;Slimewest&quot;, you step into the boots of one of six brave heroes, each with unique abilities to combat these sticky foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418870/extras/steam-img-descricao.gif?t=1728265205\" />\ud83c\udf35 <strong>Defend the Wild West! </strong>Slimes are everywhere, and it's your job to stop them.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf35 <strong>Six Heroes, Six Styles!</strong> Choose from six courageous defenders, each armed and gifted with a unique special ability.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf35 <strong>Evolve and Strengthen!</strong> With every wave defeated, every coin collected, your character grows stronger. Enhance your abilities and attributes in the game's store.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf35 <strong>Diverse Territories!</strong> Face off against different types of slimes across various challenging maps.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf35 <strong>Ascend to New Heights of Power!</strong> The further you progress, the stronger you become, readying yourself to tackle even tougher adversaries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you have what it takes to save the Wild West and become the legend of &quot;Slimewest&quot;? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418870/extras/DISCORDSLIME600.gif?t=1728265205\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418870/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728265205","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai